-- Lafarge, Holcim say in advanced merger talks
-- 
-- Fri Apr 04, 2014 11:12AM EDT
-- None



PARIS/ZURICH, April 4 (Reuters) - French and Swiss cement makers Lafarge <LAFP.PA> and Holcim <HOLN.VX> said on Friday they were in advanced discussions over a possible merger of equals, but that no agreement had yet been reached.

"Lafarge and Holcim believe that ... there is rationale in considering a potential merger that could deliver significant benefits to customers, employees and shareholders," Lafarge said in a statement.